        "body": "**Issue:** closes #<issue-number>\r\n\r\n**Popularity metric:**\r\nSimilarWeb global rank for shop.pimoroni.com: **225,478**  \r\nCategory rank: **628**  \r\nSource: https://www.similarweb.com/website/shop.pimoroni.com/#overview\r\n\r\n**Terms of Service link:**\r\nhttps://shop.pimoroni.com/pages/terms-of-service  \r\n(No restrictions preventing inclusion in Simple Icons.)\r\n\r\n### Checklist\r\n\r\n- [x] I have reviewed the forbidden brands list and confirm the brand is not listed\r\n- [x] I have reviewed the brand's terms of service and am confident we can add this icon\r\n- [x] I updated the JSON data in `data/simple-icons.json`\r\n- [x] I optimized the icon with SVGO and ensured a single path\r\n- [x] The SVG `viewbox` is `0 0 24 24`\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThis PR adds the Pimoroni brand icon.\r\n\r\n- The logo is based on the recognizable Pimoroni monkey head used across their branding.\r\n- Rebuilt and simplified as a **single SVG path** to comply with Simple Icons contribution requirements.\r\n- Normalized to a **24×24 viewBox**.\r\n- Chosen brand color: **#FF7F41**, matching Pimoroni’s dominant orange brand tone.\r\n- All tests pass successfully (`npm test` returns 0 failures).\r\n",
